text: Essam Abdel-Aziz Sharaf (, ; born 1952) is an Egyptian academic. He was the Prime Minister of Egypt from 3 March 2011 to 7 December 2011. He was Minister of Transportation from 2004 to 2005. ==References== Category:1952 births Category:Living people Category:Prime Ministers of Egypt Category:Cairo University alumni
title: Essam Sharaf
